      Subclasses of FieldType in org.jsimpledb.core 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  NullSafeType<T>
      A FieldType that wraps any other FieldType not supporting null values and adds support for null values by pre-pending to the binary encoding a 0x00 for non-null values or a 0xff byte for null values.
